Blend anchovies, oil, capers, and 1 cup parsley in a blender until a coarse pur√©e forms. Transfer to a large bowl, mix in 1/4 cup vinegar, and season with salt, pepper, and more vinegar, if desired. Add radishes, scallions, beans, olives, and remaining 1 1/2 cups parsley to bowl and toss to combine. DO AHEAD: Salad can be made 4 hours ahead. Cover and chill.